{"tid":699255,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"旺角案　法官違反陪審團","createTime":"2018-06-12T11:15:30.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-12T14:14:36.000Z","uid":47714,"like":15,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"a9773679d03b1b36211a3805465ff20751369bbc","tid":699255,"uid":47714,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-12T11:15:30.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/baggio.leung/posts/10156405364647505\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fbaggio.leung%2Fposts%2F10156405364647505&d=3k50zcR32xsrFzfRN4TQXuI2ZYfPb188nwqbwuz8hpE%3D&h=c2cd7a13\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/baggio.leung/posts/10156405364647505</a><br />\n<br />\nBaggio Leung:<br />\n<br />\n法官：「沒有爭議地，（旺角事件）當晚，食環和警察從未有驅趕小販的動作。」<br />\n<br />\n我有無聽錯？<br />\n果晚大家見鬼了？<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/lynnleiwong/posts/2184447518457994\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Flynnleiwong%2Fposts%2F2184447518457994&d=3k50zcR32xsrFzfRN4TQXuI2ZYfPb188nwqbwuz8hpE%3D&h=82a678db\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/lynnleiwong/posts/2184447518457994</a><br />\n<br />\nBaggio Leung:<br />\n<br />\n法官：「從當晚群眾的行為，我可以肯定當晚的暴動是有組織，有預謀的。」<br />\n<br />\n#肯定<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n黃鵹:<br />\n<br />\n咁係違反按陪審團裁決作 most favourable 推斷嘅規則。"},{"pid":"c0af3fe78a373b39f2a087337a81587fe5facb82","tid":699255,"uid":47714,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-12T11:15:37.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/lynnleiwong/posts/2184522541783825\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Flynnleiwong%2Fposts%2F2184522541783825&d=3k50zcR32xsrFzfRN4TQXuI2ZYfPb188nwqbwuz8hpE%3D&h=5402750a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/lynnleiwong/posts/2184522541783825</a><br />\n<br />\n黃鵹:<br />\n<br />\n終於開始有人提起「破壞社會安寧」，咁我應該澄清吓，其實呢個字係術到無得再術嘅術語，簡單來講係指「打交」，任何肢體衝突都算。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/lynnleiwong/posts/2184530411783038\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Flynnleiwong%2Fposts%2F2184530411783038&d=3k50zcR32xsrFzfRN4TQXuI2ZYfPb188nwqbwuz8hpE%3D&h=c6948f9c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/lynnleiwong/posts/2184530411783038</a><br />\n<br />\n黃鵹:<br />\n<br />\n「阻嚇」係阻嚇啲咩呢？阻嚇犯暴動罪？咁暴動罪又係乜？好簡單，你示威冇批准就係非法集結。有非法集結，差佬就可以打你，你自衛就係打交 (法定嘅虛構事實)。非法集結+打交就係暴動。<br />\n<br />\n換言之，即係「阻嚇」兩件事，行使集會嘅基本權利，行使自衛嘅基本權利。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nAragorn Ho:<br />\nbreach of the peace理論上同掛紅雨黑雨一樣，要「廣泛地區」先合理&hellip;唔通警察自己內心唔和平又關人事咩&hellip;如果內心唔和平，去信教啦&hellip;<br />\n<br />\n黃鵹:<br />\n唔關事，根本成個concept要phaseout<br />\n<br />\n黃鵹:<br />\n英國依家廢除到淨係係用來處理守行為<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/lynnleiwong/posts/2184593058443440\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Flynnleiwong%2Fposts%2F2184593058443440&d=3k50zcR32xsrFzfRN4TQXuI2ZYfPb188nwqbwuz8hpE%3D&h=bd06c14c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/lynnleiwong/posts/2184593058443440</a><br />\n<br />\n黃鵹:<br />\n<br />\n繼續有人混淆視聽。《1967年公安條例》嘅相關條文只係將普通法「暴動罪」codify，條例並無修訂/重新設立「暴動罪」。現行「暴動罪」同19世紀英格蘭法律完全一樣。<br />\n<br />\n「至於有人將本案與六七暴動的刑期比較，指本案的刑期判得比六七暴動更重，湯家驊則認為這些比較沒有特別意義，因為梁天琦等人干犯的《公安條例》是在六七暴動後才制定的。」<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/lynnleiwong/posts/2184657761770303\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Flynnleiwong%2Fposts%2F2184657761770303&d=3k50zcR32xsrFzfRN4TQXuI2ZYfPb188nwqbwuz8hpE%3D&h=d81e9ccd\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/lynnleiwong/posts/2184657761770303</a><br />\n<br />\n黃鵹:<br />\n<br />\n其實有數計。黃之鋒案，英國同樣情況量刑指引最多咪個幾月，香港就十個月，十倍。魚蛋最重嗰位我當佢承認所有控方案情，即係掟水樽啫，英國案例一大堆，大半年囉，香港七年，又係十倍。<br />\n<br />\n要阻嚇？文明世界最惡嘅咪最多兩三倍囉。十倍，唔係Star Chamber係乜？"},{"pid":"2540ea6f69130eced557552b1306f7c4ae8673